# Note on the spec and lexicons

The Emojigo language specification, lexicon templates, and Markdown container
format are released under MIT to encourage adoption.

Domain-specific lexicons contributed by individual organizations remain under
their own copyright, but should be released under permissive licenses
(MIT, Apache 2.0, CC-BY-SA) to enable cross-organization interoperability.

# Note on AI-generated contributions

This project was developed in collaboration with Claude Opus 4.6 (Anthropic).
Per Anthropic's terms, AI-generated content is released as work-for-hire
to the human author (tkman). Contributions from other AI systems should
follow each provider's terms.
